Go to jw dot org
at the top click on publications
then on the left click on videos
arrow through until you find it

Clearly Jehovah's Witnesses believe in following what the Bible says (many other popular translations KJV, NIV, etc read the same on key principles).  This dvd is applies decent moral perspectives on pertinent challenges we all encounter from time to time.  WATCH IT--if you have desire to think at all, this dvd will give you plenty to ponder along with helpful counsel.  Loved it!!!!
